      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a mechanism by which a user-interface may access a textual DAP-like interface over a TCP/IP connection.  This is a local mechanism.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify any standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
